categories: Category:Articles that are known by a nickname

nodes.text: "Lucky" was the nickname of a clone trooper who served under Captain Rex and Jedi General Anakin Skywalker.

Lucky was part of a boarding team to assist Aayla Secura's Venator-class Star Destroyer during the Sky Battle of Quell. He was killed by a mastiff phalone on Maridun while trying to find the planet's natives, whom they needed to heal General Anakin Skywalker.
